Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,不過就是個小女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅,速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開她!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼真是講不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運增幅器出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅,把他抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,我…我好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了,快撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回弗肯大人身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們,手可別停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是種幸運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遵循占卜的結果,取消了這場婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方依舊會發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我根本就不相信占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我請你做那種事,才會變成這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你也一起受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠原諒我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼下令撒退?弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要違背我的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容屬下斗膽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為再那樣下去,那些手下恐怕會有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是難以避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了我等之理想中的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,我們不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎已經發現小瞳的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定會再次發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們現在受到那個叫什麼"幸運"的保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連接近他們都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先解決掉幸運強化兵的幕後黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將背叛法尼利亞投靠多倫卡喀的那傢伙給…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的軍師弗肯·拉克魯·法尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的…王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把碗給摔破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋帶斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?這是小瞳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快,他們逃出城了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,你留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要駕駛艾斯嘉科尼去找小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親,請您睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您別留下我一個人,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我重視的人都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢出聲我就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫他們要妨礙我們打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說不准我們弄髒這座森林?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是個獸人居然搞不清楚自己的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭,貝盧貝盧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金銀雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以賣到很好的價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要這麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了梵的哥哥弗肯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你想對弗肯報恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將你帶回去給弗肯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傷成這樣,根本沒辦法再行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟亞連他們商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定能夠體諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你並不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是要我投降嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我相信你的話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有弗肯大人能讓我信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人喜歡弗肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港□?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的身影正逐漸浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻派幸運強化兵過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她尚未恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝置運作得相當順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別為我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運強化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想說如果要逃走,就一定得經由港□
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,將庫魯傑特準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在沒空應付你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是因為"幸運"嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就無法靠近現在的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裏?弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再回去弗肯那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你就搭這艘船,逃到遠方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體被奇怪的機械改造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此變得這樣虛弱殘破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是為了自己喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…這樣絕對很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就是不懂?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中潛藏的不安心情,將招來令人難過的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的意念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的意念必有實現的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信…自己的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下來會受到什麼樣的凌遲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然害怕,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想逃,明明就逃得掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信自己的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你並不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能為弗肯大人奉獻一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得心滿意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼會曉得我們所在?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,你在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你能瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念起來真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅\N什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是弗肯大人幫我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在會礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到弗肯大人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,你給我出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就是不懂呢?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們創造新世界之日就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的戰役
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就是不懂呢?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,這裏由我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運強化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不知好歹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人如此為你著想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那麼的為你著想,為何你就是不明白?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不原諒讓弗肯大人傷心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不原諒!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游要塞爆炸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,請您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能遇見您已是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠在您的目送下死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是反作用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經由人工強化的幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了名為不幸的反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次的實驗已經帶來豐碩的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是"解答"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我得到了未知的解答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我等的命運方程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把劍放下,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是我的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑翼的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:57.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:05.54,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:13.17,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:19.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:21.68,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.69,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.53,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.33,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:38.34,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.84,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:49.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:57.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:05.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:13.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:19.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:34.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:38.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

